{
  "video_id": "lWnr-99DNeE",
  "title": "The most Martian place on Earth | Armando Azua-Bustos",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12580.0,
      "end_time": 15396.0,
      "text": "This is a picture of a sunset on Mars"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15420.0,
      "end_time": 18900.0,
      "text": "taken by NASA&#39;s Curiosity rover in 2013."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19780.0,
      "end_time": 21636.0,
      "text": "Mars is a very cold planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21660.0,
      "end_time": 23916.0,
      "text": "flooded with high levels of UV radiation"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23940.0,
      "end_time": 25836.0,
      "text": "and extremely dry."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25860.0,
      "end_time": 29980.0,
      "text": "In fact, Mars is considered to be too dry for life as we know it."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30780.0,
      "end_time": 31996.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m an astrobiologist."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32200.000000000004,
      "end_time": 34916.0,
      "text": "I try to understand the origin of life on Earth"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34940.0,
      "end_time": 37156.0,
      "text": "and the possibilities of finding life"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37180.0,
      "end_time": 38420.0,
      "text": "elsewhere in the universe."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39220.0,
      "end_time": 40476.0,
      "text": "People sometimes ask me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40500.0,
      "end_time": 42676.0,
      "text": "how can you be an astrobiologist"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42700.0,
      "end_time": 44500.0,
      "text": "if you don&#39;t have your own spaceship?"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45460.0,
      "end_time": 47676.0,
      "text": "Well, what I do is that I study life"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 47700.0,
      "end_time": 49676.0,
      "text": "in those environments on Earth"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 49700.0,
      "end_time": 53200.0,
      "text": "that most closely resemble other interesting places in the universe."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 53940.0,
      "end_time": 56396.0,
      "text": "All life on Earth requires water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 56420.0,
      "end_time": 58956.0,
      "text": "so in my case I focus on the intimate relationship"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 58980.0,
      "end_time": 60476.0,
      "text": "between water and life"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 60500.0,
      "end_time": 62760.0,
      "text": "in order to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 62100.0,
      "end_time": 65340.0,
      "text": "if we could find life in a planet as dry as Mars."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66260.0,
      "end_time": 69796.0,
      "text": "But since I do not have the 2.5 billion dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 69820.0,
      "end_time": 72350.0,
      "text": "to send my own robot to Mars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 72600.0,
      "end_time": 74996.0,
      "text": "I study the most Martian place on Earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 75200.0,
      "end_time": 76556.0,
      "text": "the Atacama Desert."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 76580.0,
      "end_time": 78236.0,
      "text": "Located in northern Chile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78260.0,
      "end_time": 81876.0,
      "text": "it is the oldest and driest desert on Earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81900.0,
      "end_time": 83876.0,
      "text": "To give you an idea of how dry it is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 83900.0,
      "end_time": 88940.0,
      "text": "consider here in Vancouver it rains over 1,000 millimeters of rain every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 89700.0,
      "end_time": 93316.0,
      "text": "In the Atacama, there are places with no reported rains"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 93340.0,
      "end_time": 95140.0,
      "text": "in the last 400 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 96700.0,
      "end_time": 98396.0,
      "text": "How do I know this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 98420.0,
      "end_time": 101916.0,
      "text": "Well, because I was born and raised in the Atacama --"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 101940.0,
      "end_time": 103556.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 103580.0,
      "end_time": 105596.0,
      "text": "So I had a unique advantage"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 105620.0,
      "end_time": 107660.0,
      "text": "when I started studying this desert."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 108700.0,
      "end_time": 112236.0,
      "text": "So let me tell you guys a few fantastic examples"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 112260.0,
      "end_time": 113916.0,
      "text": "he has found"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 113940.0,
      "end_time": 117140.0,
      "text": "on how life has adapted to live with almost no water at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 118460.0,
      "end_time": 121350.0,
      "text": "One of my first findings was in the entrance of a cave"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 121600.0,
      "end_time": 122796.0,
      "text": "facing the Pacific Ocean."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 122820.0,
      "end_time": 126515.0,
      "text": "In this place, we reported a new type of microalgae"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 126540.0,
      "end_time": 130460.0,
      "text": "that grew only on top of the spiderwebs that covered the cave entrance."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 131600.0,
      "end_time": 133580.0,
      "text": "Have you ever seen a spiderweb early in the morning?"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 135200.0,
      "end_time": 136596.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s covered with dew,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 136620.0,
      "end_time": 139876.0,
      "text": "so this microalgae learned that in order to carry photosynthesis"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 139900.0,
      "end_time": 142916.0,
      "text": "in the coast of the driest desert on Earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 142940.0,
      "end_time": 144436.0,
      "text": "they could use the spiderwebs."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 144460.0,
      "end_time": 146876.0,
      "text": "So here they may access the water from the fogs"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 146900.0,
      "end_time": 149140.0,
      "text": "that regularly cover these areas in the morning."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 150460.0,
      "end_time": 153300.0,
      "text": "In another cave, we found a different type of microalgae."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 153940.0,
      "end_time": 158156.0,
      "text": "This one is able to use ocean mist as a source of water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 158180.0,
      "end_time": 161316.0,
      "text": "and strikingly lives in the very bottom of a cave,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 161340.0,
      "end_time": 164556.0,
      "text": "so it has adapted to live with less than 0.1 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 164580.0,
      "end_time": 167700.0,
      "text": "of the amount of light that regular plants need."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 168820.0,
      "end_time": 171835.0,
      "text": "These type of findings suggest to me that on Mars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 171860.0,
      "end_time": 174716.0,
      "text": "we may find even photosynthetic life inside caves."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 174740.0,
      "end_time": 176116.0,
      "text": "And by the way, that&#39;s me."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 176140.0,
      "end_time": 178956.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 178980.0,
      "end_time": 184715.0,
      "text": "Now, for almost 15 years this region of Yungay, discovered by NASA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 184740.0,
      "end_time": 187756.0,
      "text": "was thought to be the driest place of this desert,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 187780.0,
      "end_time": 189516.0,
      "text": "but I knew that it was not."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 189540.0,
      "end_time": 191916.0,
      "text": "How? You already know the answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 191940.0,
      "end_time": 194156.0,
      "text": "Because I was born and raised in this desert."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 194180.0,
      "end_time": 198836.0,
      "text": "So I remembered that I usually see fogs in Yungay,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 198860.0,
      "end_time": 201760.0,
      "text": "so after setting sensors in a number of places,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 201100.0,
      "end_time": 204156.0,
      "text": "where I remember never seeing fogs or clouds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 204180.0,
      "end_time": 208196.0,
      "text": "I reported four other sites much drier than Yungay,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 208220.0,
      "end_time": 210836.0,
      "text": "with this one, Mar√≠a Elena South,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 210860.0,
      "end_time": 214316.0,
      "text": "being the truly driest place on Earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 214340.0,
      "end_time": 216316.0,
      "text": "as dry as Mars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 216340.0,
      "end_time": 218676.0,
      "text": "and amazingly, just a 15-minute ride"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 218700.0,
      "end_time": 220980.0,
      "text": "from the small mining town where I was born."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 221820.0,
      "end_time": 225236.0,
      "text": "Now, in this search, we were trying to actually find the dry limit"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 225260.0,
      "end_time": 226476.0,
      "text": "for life on Earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 226500.0,
      "end_time": 230356.0,
      "text": "a place so dry that nothing was able to survive in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 230380.0,
      "end_time": 232956.0,
      "text": "But even here, well hidden underground,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 232980.0,
      "end_time": 235396.0,
      "text": "we found a number of different microorganisms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 235420.0,
      "end_time": 238875.0,
      "text": "which suggested to me that similarly dry places, like Mars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 238900.0,
      "end_time": 240100.0,
      "text": "may be in inhabited."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 241180.0,
      "end_time": 243476.0,
      "text": "We even have some preliminary evidences"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 243500.0,
      "end_time": 246360.0,
      "text": "that these microorganisms may still be active"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 246600.0,
      "end_time": 247996.0,
      "text": "in the desiccated state,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 248200.0,
      "end_time": 251836.0,
      "text": "like walking mummies all around us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 251860.0,
      "end_time": 255980.0,
      "text": "and that they may be using UV radiation as a source of energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 256700.0,
      "end_time": 261276.0,
      "text": "If confirmed, this would have a huge impact on our definition of life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 261300.0,
      "end_time": 263820.0,
      "text": "on how we look for life elsewhere in the universe."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 264580.0,
      "end_time": 267596.0,
      "text": "Due to its clear skies, by 2020,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 267620.0,
      "end_time": 270276.0,
      "text": "60 percent of the biggest telescopes on Earth"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 270300.0,
      "end_time": 272516.0,
      "text": "will be located in the Atacama,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 272540.0,
      "end_time": 275436.0,
      "text": "and while everyone else will be looking among the stars"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 275460.0,
      "end_time": 277700.0,
      "text": "to answer the question, \"Are we alone?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 278620.0,
      "end_time": 280516.0,
      "text": "I will be looking down to the ground"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 280540.0,
      "end_time": 283116.0,
      "text": "searching for this same answer"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 283140.0,
      "end_time": 284340.0,
      "text": "in my own backyard."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 284780.0,
      "end_time": 285996.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 286200.0,
      "end_time": 289180.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}